    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes synchronization mechanisms for public
   repositories as part of the Authenticated Transfer Protocol (ATP).
   It specifies both a low-latency streaming protocol over WebSocket,
   and a full-repository fetch mechanism over HTTP.</t>
